-- Dollar Drops to 15-Year Low Versus Yen as Private Companies Eliminate Jobs
-- B y   A l l i s o n   B e n n e t t
-- 2010-10-06T12:18:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-06/dollar-drops-to-15-year-low-versus-yen-as-private-companies-eliminate-jobs.html
The dollar fell against the euro and
the yen after a private report based on payrolls showed job
losses in September, adding to concern about the pace of the
U.S. economy. The dollar touched a 15-year low against the yen.  To contact the reporter on this story:
